{"word":"Cymbal","slug":"cymbal","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Cymbal</b> A musical instrument.<br/> Of brass<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=19'>1Ch 15:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=28'>1Ch 15:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=13&verse=1'>1Co 13:1</a><br/> Used in the tabernacle service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=5'>2Sa 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=13&verse=8'>1Ch 13:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=16'>1Ch 15:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=19'>1Ch 15:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=28'>1Ch 15:28</a><br/> Used in the temple service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=5&verse=13'>2Ch 5:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=5'>1Ch 16:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=42'>1Ch 16:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=1'>1Ch 25:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=6'>1Ch 25:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=150&verse=5'>Psa 150:5</a><br/> Used on special occasions:<br/> - Day of atonement<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=25'>2Ch 29:25</a> <br/> - Laying of the foundation of the second temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=11'>Ezr 3:11</a> <br/> - Dedication of the wall<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=27'>Neh 12:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=36'>Neh 12:36</a> "}]}